SELECT
  $__timeInterval(timestamp) AS time,
  quantile(0.5)(toUInt64(data.slot_landed) - toUInt64(data.slot_sent)) AS p50,
  quantile(0.95)(toUInt64(data.slot_landed) - toUInt64(data.slot_sent)) AS p95,
  quantile(0.99)(toUInt64(data.slot_landed) - toUInt64(data.slot_sent)) AS p99,
  max(toUInt64(data.slot_landed) - toUInt64(data.slot_sent)) AS max
FROM clickhouse_logs.slot_latency
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(timestamp)
  AND data.slot_sent IS NOT NULL
  AND data.slot_landed IS NOT NULL
  AND toUInt64(data.slot_landed) >= toUInt64(data.slot_sent)
  AND match(toString(data.host), '${host:regex}')
  AND match(toString(data.staked), '${staked:regex}')
  AND match(toString(data.api_key), '${api_key:regex}')
GROUP BY time
ORDER BY time

SELECT
  $__timeInterval(timestamp) AS time,
  quantile(0.5)(toUInt64(data.position_in_block)) AS p50,
  quantile(0.95)(toUInt64(data.position_in_block)) AS p95,
  quantile(0.99)(toUInt64(data.position_in_block)) AS p99
FROM clickhouse_logs.slot_latency
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(timestamp)
  AND data.position_in_block IS NOT NULL
  AND data.slot_sent IS NOT NULL
  AND match(toString(data.host), '${host:regex}')
  AND match(toString(data.staked), '${staked:regex}')
  AND match(toString(data.api_key), '${api_key:regex}')
GROUP BY time
ORDER BY time

SELECT
  toStartOfInterval(timestamp, INTERVAL 10 second) AS time,
  (count(*) / 10) as request_rate,
  toString(data.method) as method,
  toString(data.failed) as failed
FROM clickhouse_logs.requests
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(timestamp)
  AND match(toString(data.host), '${host:regex}')
  AND match(toString(data.staked), '${staked:regex}')
  AND match(toString(data.api_key), '${api_key:regex}')
GROUP BY time, method, failed
ORDER BY time

SELECT
  toStartOfInterval(timestamp, INTERVAL 10 second) AS time,
  max(toUInt64(data.latency_ms)) as max_latency_ms,
  toString(data.method) as method,
  toString(data.failed) as failed
FROM clickhouse_logs.requests
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(timestamp)
  AND match(toString(data.host), '${host:regex}')
  AND match(toString(data.staked), '${staked:regex}')
  AND match(toString(data.api_key), '${api_key:regex}')
GROUP BY time, method, failed
ORDER BY time

SELECT
  toStartOfInterval(timestamp, INTERVAL 60 second) AS time,
  (count(*) / 60) as request_rate,
  toString(data.endpoint_name) as endpoint_name
FROM clickhouse_logs.metrics
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(timestamp)
  AND data.metric = 'txn_send_loop_ns'
  AND match(toString(data.host), '${host:regex}')
  AND match(toString(data.staked), '${staked:regex}')
  -- and data.is_current_leader = 'true'
GROUP BY time,endpoint_name
ORDER BY time

SELECT
  toStartOfInterval(timestamp, INTERVAL 60 second) AS time,
  max(toUInt64(data.time_ns)) as time_ns,
  toString(data.relay_destination) as relay_destination,
  toString(data.host) as host
FROM clickhouse_logs.metrics
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(timestamp)
  and data.metric = 'sendTransactionRelay'
  AND match(toString(data.host), '${host:regex}')
  AND match(toString(data.staked), '${staked:regex}')
  AND match(toString(data.api_key), '${api_key:regex}')
GROUP BY time, relay_destination, host
ORDER BY time

SELECT
  toStartOfInterval(timestamp, INTERVAL 1 second) AS time,

WHERE
  $__timeFilter(timestamp)

  AND match(toString(data.host), '${host:regex}')
  AND match(toString(data.staked), '${staked:regex}')

ORDER BY time

SELECT
  $__timeInterval(timestamp) AS time,
  max(toUInt64(data.time_to_start_sending_ns)) AS max_time_to_start_sending_ns,
  toString(data.qos_priority) as qos_priority
FROM clickhouse_logs.txn_sender_logs
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(timestamp)
  AND data.time_to_start_sending_ns IS NOT NULL
  AND match(toString(data.datacenter), '${datacenter:regex}')
  AND match(toString(data.staked), '${staked:regex}')
  AND match(toString(data.host), '${host:regex}')
  AND match(toString(data.is_retry), '${is_retry:regex}')
  AND match(toString(data.dropped), '${dropped:regex}')
  AND match(toString(data.api_key), '${api_key:regex}')
  AND data.is_retry = false
GROUP BY time, qos_priority
ORDER BY time

SELECT
  $__timeInterval(timestamp) AS time,
  -- quantile(0.5)(toUInt64(data.path.rtt_micros)) AS p50,
  -- quantile(0.95)(toUInt64(data.path.rtt_micros)) AS p95,
  max(toUInt64(data.path.rtt_micros)) AS p99,
  toString(data.identity) as identity
FROM clickhouse_logs.validator_quic_metrics
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(timestamp)
  AND data.path.rtt_micros IS NOT NULL
  AND match(toString(data.host), '${host:regex}')
  AND match(toString(data.staked), '${staked:regex}')
GROUP BY time,identity
ORDER BY time

SELECT
  toStartOfInterval(timestamp, INTERVAL 1 second) AS time,
  sum(toUInt64(data.queue_at_end)) as num_dropped,
  toString(data.endpoint_name) as endpoint_name
FROM clickhouse_logs.metrics
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(timestamp)
  AND data.metric = 'connection_loop_total_time_ns'
  AND match(toString(data.host), '${host:regex}')
  AND match(toString(data.staked), '${staked:regex}')
GROUP BY time,endpoint_name
ORDER BY time

SELECT
  $__timeInterval(timestamp) AS time,
  count(*) as num_failed,
  toString(data.txn_strategy) as txn_strategy
FROM clickhouse_logs.slot_latency
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(timestamp)
  AND toBool(data.failed) = true
  AND toUInt64(data.slot_landed) >= toUInt64(data.slot_sent)
  AND match(toString(data.host), '${host:regex}')
  AND match(toString(data.staked), '${staked:regex}')
  AND match(toString(data.api_key), '${api_key:regex}')
GROUP BY time,txn_strategy
ORDER BY time

SELECT 
    toStartOfHour(timestamp) as time,
    CAST(tip.data.provider AS String) as metric,
    (SUM(CASE WHEN bundles.is_bundle = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 100.0) / COUNT(*) as value
FROM clickhouse_logs.txn_monitor_tip_logs tip
INNER JOIN clickhouse_logs.bundles bundles 
    ON CAST(tip.data.signature AS String) = bundles.signature
WHERE $__timeFilter(timestamp)
  AND CAST(tip.data.provider AS String) IS NOT NULL
  AND CAST(tip.data.provider AS String) != ''
  AND CAST(tip.data.tip_amount AS String) != ''
  AND CAST(tip.data.tip_amount AS String) != '0'
  AND toInt64OrNull(CAST(tip.data.tip_amount AS String)) IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY 
    toStartOfHour(timestamp),
    CAST(tip.data.provider AS String)
ORDER BY time, metric;

SELECT
  signature,
  toString(data.leader_sent) AS leader_sent,
  toString(data.leaders_landed) AS leader_landed,
  toUInt64(data.slot_sent) AS slot_sent,
  toUInt64(data.slot_landed) AS slot_landed,
  toUInt64(data.slot_landed) - toUInt64(data.slot_sent) AS slot_latency,
  toUInt64(data.latency_ns) / 1000000 AS latency_ms,
  toUInt64(data.priority) AS priority,
  timestamp
FROM clickhouse_logs.slot_latency
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(timestamp)
  AND data.slot_landed IS NOT NULL
  AND data.slot_sent IS NOT NULL
  AND data.leader_sent IS NOT NULL
  AND data.leaders_landed IS NOT NULL
  AND data.latency_ns IS NOT NULL
  AND data.latency_ns > 0
  and slot_latency > 2
  AND match(toString(data.host), '${host:regex}')
  AND match(toString(data.staked), '${staked:regex}')
  AND match(toString(data.api_key), '${api_key:regex}')
ORDER BY slot_latency DESC
